/* eslint-disable template-curly-spacing */
 
import {css} from "emotion";
 
import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";
import flaggedStyles from "../../../utils/flagged-styles";
import getSiteVars from "../site.var";
import {darken,makeReadable} from "../../../utils/css-utils";
 
export default styleMemoize((flags,variation)=>{
 
  const siteVars = getSiteVars();
 
  const {
    getColor,
    firstReadableColor,
    // basicBorderSize,
  } = siteVars;
 
  const color = getColor(variation);
 
  return flaggedStyles(flags,{
 
    _: ()=>(css`
      background-color: ${color};
      color: ${firstReadableColor(color,["#ffffff",makeReadable(color,color)])};
    `),
 
    basic: ()=>(css`
      background-color: transparent;
      border: 1px solid ${darken(color,10)};
      color: ${makeReadable(color)};
    `)
  });
});
